title: Living Without Crutches | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Living Without Crutches | Joel Osteen
description:
Some people were only meant to be in our lives for a season. We have to be wise enough to recognize when their part in our story is over. The good news is, when God closes a door, it's because He has something better in store.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
